tr.td:
Hi Laura,
You explained in your questionnaire that you were interested in starting the copper IUD.
Unfortunately we were not able to speak despite waiting 5 mins and also calling you twice.
Please kindly rebook an appointment to further discuss this. Typically copper coils and arranged via locally via sexual health clinic.
John Scott Health Centre in Manor House have a sexual health service linked to Homerton hospital if local to you. This runs 9am to 4pm.
Kind regards, Colina PA-R
